 2003-03672003-03-25,  PCO,  ,  , 
ActPublic Service Staff Relations Act
PrecisRe-appointment of YVON TARTE of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Chairperson of the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of three years; and orders that he shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective May 7, 2003.
